            <title>[FLINK-36511] FlinkSecurityManager#checkExit StackOverFlow if haltOnSystemExit is enabled</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FLINK-36511</link>
                <project id="12315522" key="FLINK">Flink</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The halt() call in checkExit() will again cause checkExit() to be called since we don&apos;t null the security manager, in contrast to how forceProcessExit is implemented.&lt;br/&gt;
